data.description: This beautifully spacious home in Lawson Farms has exactly what you need to give you much-needed balance. Boasting enormous versatility with a media-game room, a home office (which could be another bedroom itself), as well as a formal dining room or den. The endless possibilities of this layout provide you with plenty of breathing room while still allowing you the privacy of split bedrooms and more than enough space for everyone to call their own. The natural light cascading from the open-island kitchen skylight accentuates the beautiful white cabinets, stainless appliances, and the perfectly proportional contrast of the black granite countertops. Take comfort in the security and convenience of the smart-home features indoors or embrace the numerous amenities outdoors.
